# Recruitment Plan Controller Endpoints
# Base URL: http://localhost:3001
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Create plan (protected)
POST http://localhost:3001/recruitment-plans
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Kế hoạch quý 1/2026",
  "startDate": "2026-01-01",
  "endDate": "2026-03-31"
}

### Get all plans (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/recruitment-plans
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Get plan by ID (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/recruitment-plans/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Update/Approve plan (protected)
PATCH http://localhost:3001/recruitment-plans/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "status": "APPROVED"
}

### Delete plan (protected)
DELETE http://localhost:3001/recruitment-plans/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
